#: ../../source/usage/multiple_environments.md:3
msgid ""
"IR-SIM supports creating and running multiple environments simultaneously. "
"Each environment maintains its own isolated state, including world "
"parameters, objects, and simulation time. This is useful for:"
msgstr ""
